{"tid":307431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"精液量世界第一的男人　讓AV變成搞笑片","createTime":"2017-07-03T11:06:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T11:10:54.000Z","uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"45b75c35968fdc150829e41e355bf475cc17cbee","tid":307431,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T11:06:45.000Z","msg":"2017年07月03日00:00<br />\n<br />\nAV片裡面潮吹用水管灌水代替、用自製液體代替精液做效果的事情早就屢見不鮮，不過有時候玩得太誇張就會變成搞笑片讓人軟棒看歡樂的。<br />\n<br />\n日本AV廠商「Rookie」，除了推出「跟噴出世界第一精液量的男人啪啪啪」系列，讓粉絲看得不要不要的後，又想出了新花招，推出新作「跟將保險套灌到最滿的男人啪啪啪」，白色牛奶的量，裝起來比一顆西瓜還要大。讓日本網友紛紛吐槽「已經變綜藝節目了」、「女優不會笑場也很厲害」，或是反串「這是真的！世界是很廣大的」。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170703/640_44bc65350ce9ea8f21afeadb84f41d70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170703%2F640_44bc65350ce9ea8f21afeadb84f41d70.jpg&h=770b7718&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翻攝自網路<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170703/420_993e920bda4ff7749b03945d08e4e338.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170703%2F420_993e920bda4ff7749b03945d08e4e338.jpg&h=b2f03fcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翻攝自網路<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170703/420_9b57e7d6774ff472db1c0eaf30a6f475.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170703%2F420_9b57e7d6774ff472db1c0eaf30a6f475.jpg&h=6858125e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翻攝自網路<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170703/1152836/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170703%2F1152836%2F&d=oLu6SYbpovQwdNbJOYlgES7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=48990fc1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170703/1152836/</a>"},{"pid":"6648556ccb459d49175d9491